@startuml Process_Activity_View
title Process Activity View: Assessment Lifecycle

|User|
start
:Choose Model & Reasoning Mode;
:Select PDF Document;
:Execute "Upload & Run Assessment";

|Backend (Ingestion)|
:Receive Multi-part File;
:Extract Text (PyMuPDF);
:Capture Metadata (Source, Page, Chapter);
:Chunk & Embed;
:Upsert to ChromaDB;

|Backend (Orchestrator)|
:Initialize Assessment Pipeline;
:Load Framework Schema (criteria_new.json);
while (Next Criterion in JSON?) is (Yes)
    :Generate Semantic Query (Requirement + Keywords);
    :Retrieve Top-K Evidence Chunks (Filter >= 0.3 or Top-3 Fallback);
    
    :Assemble Context (Assessment Question + Requirement + Expected Evidence + Rubric + Evidence);
    if (Mode == "Triple"?) then (True)
        :Step 1: Conceptual Alignment;
        :Step 2: Gap Analysis;
        :Step 3: Synthesis & Verification;
    else (False)
        :Single Agent (3-in-1 Prompting);
    endif
    :Evaluate Compliance Classification (e.g., NOT_EVIDENCED);
    
    :Map Status to Numeric Score (1.0 / 0.5 / 0.0);
endwhile (Done)

:Compute Aggregated Compliance Score;
:Generate & Archive JSON Report;

|Frontend|
:Display Real-time Results;
:Render History & Dashboard;
stop

@enduml
